    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to share my pride and joy with you. Honestly, this car is an absolute dream and still looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and is in truly pristine shape\u2014not a single detail missed. You\u2019ve gotta see it in person to believe how clean it is! Feel free to reach out with any questions at all; I\u2019d love for this beauty to go to a great new home!",
