    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in exceptional mechanical order. This example features the S54B32 inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The high-revving valvetrain has been meticulously maintained, with a documented VANOS overhaul and proactive rod bearing replacement already completed. The chassis remains structurally flawless, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a factory limited-slip differential that retains its original locking characteristics. Finished in original paint with zero oxidation and an interior devoid of bolster wear, this specimen represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-division engineering.",
