    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior finish retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings, thanks to a professional ceramic coating applied annually. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple without a single crease or sign of bolster wear, and it still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the adaptive cruise control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is peerless. It comes with a binder of every service receipt, showing oil changes every 3,000 miles and a recent comprehensive multi-point inspection that returned a perfect score. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road salt or debris. Riding on a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport tires, the drive is whisper-quiet and perfectly balanced. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for the most discerning buyer who demands perfection.",
